00:15:17,040 --> 00:15:19,950
THANKS. I LOOK FORWARD
TO STARTING FOR YOU, SIR.

259
00:15:20,010 --> 00:15:20,880
HEY.

260
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:24,650
WELL, WELCOME
TO ATHENS.

261
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:27,750
SEE, EVER SINCE
I WAS LITTLE,

