00:15:27,820 --> 00:15:28,950
I'VE BEEN
LOOKIN' FORWARD

263
00:15:29,020 --> 00:15:30,690
TO SENIOR SEASON.

264
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:32,630
AND EVER SINCE
I WAS LITTLE,

265
00:15:32,690 --> 00:15:35,660
I HAVE BEEN WEARING
NUMBER 40.

266
00:15:35,730 --> 00:15:37,750
SEE, TRADITION IS,

