00:15:59,490 --> 00:16:01,150
YOU COULD HAVE IT BACK.

276
00:16:01,220 --> 00:16:03,020
JUST HANG ON
FOR ONE SECOND.

277
00:16:03,070 --> 00:16:06,390
SEE, NOW,
YOU'RE NEW. I'M NOT,

278
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,930
BUT I AM ONE
HECK OF A NICE GUY,

279
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:08,990
SO HERE'S
WHAT I'M GONNA DO.

280
00:16:09,060 --> 00:16:10,500
I'M JUST GONNA GIVE
YOU A LITTLE BIT

281
00:16:10,570 --> 00:16:12,030
OF FREE ADVICE, OK?

282
00:16:13,700 --> 00:16:15,440
DON'T TUG
ON SUPERMAN'S CAPE.

283
00:16:17,090 --> 00:16:18,390
I DON'T NEED TO.

284
00:16:18,460 --> 00:16:20,870
I'M THE ONE
HOLDING IT.

285
00:16:20,940 --> 00:16:22,410
I FORGOT
TO TELL YOU BOYS

286
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:24,610
MAKE SURE
THEY KNOW AT HOME

287
00:16:24,680 --> 00:16:26,410
ABOUT THE DOUBLE-DAYS
ON MONDAY.

288
00:16:28,620 --> 00:16:34,250
AND IF I HEAR ABOUT ANY
ALTERCATIONS IN THE RANKS,

289
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:37,160
TRUMAN DEALT MORE MERCY
