00:17:52,630 --> 00:17:56,040
WE CLOSE DOWN
FOR FOOTBALL.

296
00:17:56,100 --> 00:17:58,540
AHH.
SURE IS NICE

297
00:17:58,610 --> 00:17:59,540
TO BE ABLE
TO LEAVE EARLY.

298
00:18:01,910 --> 00:18:03,310
GOOD HAVIN' YOU
AROUND.

299
00:18:05,180 --> 00:18:06,080
THANKS, TEE.

