00:18:34,340 --> 00:18:35,210
TEE?

306
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:38,610
TEE, ARE YOU HERE?

307
00:18:42,550 --> 00:18:45,690
Elvis:
DECEMBER 12, 1965.

