00:19:05,910 --> 00:19:09,880
AN 80-YARD STREAM PASS.

315
00:19:09,940 --> 00:19:11,680
HUT, HUT, HUT!

316
00:19:13,480 --> 00:19:15,010
OH, YEAH!

317
00:19:15,080 --> 00:19:18,750
TOUCHDOWN 2 IS A 21-YARD
TEAR THROUGH 4 DEFENDERS

318
00:19:18,820 --> 00:19:20,490
AT LIGHTNING SPEED.

