00:19:22,270 --> 00:19:25,660
TOUCHDOWNS 3, 4, AND 5
ARE VINTAGE ELVIS.

320
00:19:25,730 --> 00:19:27,830
JUKING, HIGH-STEPPING,
WHO'S YOUR DADDY?

321
00:19:27,900 --> 00:19:29,580
LINING FEVER DREAMS.
YOU ARE, ELVIS.

322
00:19:29,650 --> 00:19:30,960
OPEN FIELD.

323
00:19:31,030 --> 00:19:32,830
THAT'S RIGHT.
IMPROV, BABY.

324
00:19:32,900 --> 00:19:34,200
GALE SAYERS WITNESSES...

325
00:19:34,270 --> 00:19:35,230
IN HIS PRIME.

326
00:19:35,290 --> 00:19:38,400
WISHES HE COULD KEEP
WITH THIS WILD BUCK!

327
00:19:38,470 --> 00:19:39,470
BUT THE SIXTH--

328
00:19:39,540 --> 00:19:40,590
OH, BABY--

329
00:19:40,660 --> 00:19:43,280
THE SIXTH
AND FINAL TOUCHDOWN

330
00:19:43,340 --> 00:19:44,590
IS A THING OF BEAUTY.

331
00:19:44,660 --> 00:19:46,680
AN 85-YARD PUNT RETURN.

332
00:19:48,150 --> 00:19:49,080
OH, HE'S GOT IT.

333
00:19:49,150 --> 00:19:50,520
OH, MY GOD!

334
00:19:50,590 --> 00:19:52,280
TOUCHDOWN!

335
00:19:52,350 --> 00:19:55,690
OH, YEAH! UH-HUH! UH-HUH!

336
00:19:55,760 --> 00:19:58,660
BOOM! GRR!

337
00:19:58,730 --> 00:20:00,360
GRR!

338
00:20:02,060 --> 00:20:03,160
[GASPS]

339
00:20:04,580 --> 00:20:07,330
I WAS JUST
LOOKING FOR TEE...

340
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:11,270
AND...DEFINITELY
NOT UNDER HERE.

341
00:20:16,910 --> 00:20:18,710
I'M RACHEL.

342
00:20:18,780 --> 00:20:21,080
YOUR F.C.A.
PRAYER WARRIOR.

343
00:20:25,420 --> 00:20:26,790
NO. I KEEP
YOUR GAME HELMET

344
00:20:26,850 --> 00:20:27,790
TILL FRIDAY NIGHT.

345
00:20:27,860 --> 00:20:29,890
IT'S KIND OF
A VISUAL REMINDER

346
00:20:29,960 --> 00:20:32,160
THAT I NEED
TO PRAY FOR YOU.

347
00:20:32,230 --> 00:20:34,130
I DO OK ON MY OWN.

348
00:20:39,330 --> 00:20:42,430
A GENTLEMAN
WOULD WALK ME HOME.

349
00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:44,200
LET ME KNOW
WHEN YOU FIND ONE.

350
00:20:45,670 --> 00:20:46,560
HEY, ELVIS.

351
00:20:50,110 --> 00:20:51,710
I JUST WANTED
TO MAKE SURE

352
00:20:51,780 --> 00:20:53,750
THAT THAT WAS
REALLY YOUR NAME.

353
00:20:55,450 --> 00:20:56,380
CUTE.

354
00:20:56,450 --> 00:20:59,890
SEE? I KNEW YOU HAD
A SENSE OF HUMOR.

355
00:21:02,140 --> 00:21:04,020
YOU MIGHT AS WELL FACE IT.

356
00:21:04,090 --> 00:21:07,030
YOU'RE STUCK WITH ME
FOR THE REST OF THE SEASON.

357
00:21:07,100 --> 00:21:09,230
THAT IS,
IF YOU MAKE IT THAT LONG.

358
00:21:09,300 --> 00:21:10,330
"IF"?

359
00:21:10,400 --> 00:21:11,900
OH, I KNOW WHY
GUYS LIKE YOU

360
00:21:11,970 --> 00:21:13,370
COME TO ATHENS.

361
00:21:13,430 --> 00:21:15,130
HA HA.

362
00:21:15,200 --> 00:21:16,540
I HATE TO BREAK IT TO YOU,

363
00:21:16,600 --> 00:21:21,270
BUT BRIAN, THE GUY
WHOSE JERSEY YOU COMMANDEERED,

364
00:21:21,340 --> 00:21:22,840
HE'S A SHOO-IN
FOR THE SCHOLARSHIP,

365
00:21:22,910 --> 00:21:24,440
THE COACH'S NEPHEW.

366
00:21:24,510 --> 00:21:26,250
EVERY ONE OF THE SCHULERS

367
00:21:26,310 --> 00:21:28,350
HAVE GONE TO 'BAMA
SINCE BEAR BRYANT.

368
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:29,920
MAYBE THIS AIN'T
HIS YEAR.

369
00:21:34,490 --> 00:21:36,990
SO...

370
00:21:37,060 --> 00:21:38,320
WHAT SHOULD I PRAY FOR?

371
00:21:46,070 --> 00:21:47,500
GREEN GRASS.

372
00:21:50,810 --> 00:21:51,670
OK.

373
00:22:04,520 --> 00:22:05,620
Coach Schuler: DOGS,

374
00:22:05,690 --> 00:22:07,020
PASSING FOOTBALL

375
00:22:07,090 --> 00:22:10,290
LIVES BY 3
OF GOD'S LOST COMMANDMENTS.

376
00:22:10,360 --> 00:22:13,960
COMMANDMENT 1: THOU SHALT
RUN THE WISHBONE OFFENSE.

377
00:22:14,030 --> 00:22:19,250
COMMANDMENT 2: THOU SHALT
NEVER FUMBLE MY BALL.

378
00:22:19,320 --> 00:22:20,330
COMMANDMENT 3:

379
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:23,040
THOU SHALT DO IT MY WAY
ALL THE TIME!

380
00:22:23,100 --> 00:22:24,250
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

381
00:22:24,320 --> 00:22:26,310
YOU A CRUSHER, GO ON, MOVE!

382
00:22:26,370 --> 00:22:27,740
[BLOWS WHISTLE]

383
00:22:27,810 --> 00:22:29,910
WITH APOCALYPTIC FORCE!

384
00:22:29,960 --> 00:22:30,940
[BLOWS WHISTLE]

385
00:22:33,450 --> 00:22:35,010
TO THE NUTS,
DOGS!

386
00:22:35,080 --> 00:22:36,620
THE MARROW
OF THE BONE!

387
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:37,550
[BLOWS WHISTLE]

388
00:22:52,100 --> 00:22:53,530
AW.

389
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:54,870
[ALL LAUGH]

390
00:22:56,320 --> 00:22:57,600
85!

391
00:22:58,940 --> 00:22:59,910
21!

392
00:22:59,970 --> 00:23:01,240
49!

393
00:23:02,690 --> 00:23:03,580
40!

394
00:23:06,650 --> 00:23:07,580
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

395
00:23:07,650 --> 00:23:09,850
YOU ALL HEAR THAT, HUH?

396
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:10,850
THAT'S THE FIRST TIME

397
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:12,150
I HEARD
THE BIG BANG ALL DAY!

398
00:23:12,220 --> 00:23:14,150
THAT'S THE SOUND
OF PERCUSSION!

399
00:23:14,220 --> 00:23:16,210
YOU A TOUGH GUY,
JACKSON?

400
00:23:16,270 --> 00:23:17,690
NO, SIR.

401
00:23:17,760 --> 00:23:18,690
SAY AGAIN?

402
00:23:18,760 --> 00:23:20,330
NO, SIR,
I JUST WANT MY TURN.

403
00:23:20,380 --> 00:23:22,630
YOU FLOSS
WITH BARBED WIRE

404
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:24,210
AND GARGLE
WITH GASOLINE, BOY?

405
00:23:26,280 --> 00:23:28,030
55!

406
00:23:28,100 --> 00:23:30,290
21!

407
00:23:30,350 --> 00:23:31,640
13!

408
00:23:31,710 --> 00:23:33,240
TAKE HIM DOWN!
THAT'S 42!

409
00:23:37,030 --> 00:23:39,540
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

410
00:23:39,610 --> 00:23:40,980
ALL RIGHT, LADIES,
THAT'S ENOUGH.

411
00:23:44,520 --> 00:23:45,720
Coach Schuler:
HEY, HEY!

412
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:50,170
BACK OFF! BACK OFF!
CLEAR OUT! CLEAR OUT!

413
00:23:50,240 --> 00:23:53,690
CLEAR OUT!
HEY, IT'S OVER!

414
00:23:53,760 --> 00:23:57,360
GET UP! GET UP!

415
00:23:57,430 --> 00:23:59,360
WHERE'S
YOUR DISCIPLINE, SON?

416
00:23:59,430 --> 00:24:01,430
IT'S OVER!

417
00:24:01,500 --> 00:24:02,670
WHAT'S GOIN' ON HERE?

418
00:24:02,740 --> 00:24:04,250
ANYONE WANT TO TELL ME

419
00:24:04,340 --> 00:24:06,440
WHY TWO OF MY PLAYERS
IN A HEAD-ON COLLISION?

420
00:24:06,510 --> 00:24:08,670
SIR, IT WAS ELVIS.

421
00:24:08,740 --> 00:24:09,940
HE STARTED IT.

422
00:24:10,010 --> 00:24:12,440
WHY, THANK YOU, SON.

423
00:24:12,510 --> 00:24:13,510
YOU CAN GO HOME NOW.

424
00:24:13,580 --> 00:24:14,680
YOU'RE OFF THIS TEAM.

425
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:15,880
GO ON, NOW.

426
00:24:15,950 --> 00:24:17,050
ANYONE ELSE?

427
00:24:17,120 --> 00:24:19,320
WANT TO TELL ME
WHAT HAPPENED?

428
00:24:19,390 --> 00:24:20,750
COME ON, NOW, COME ON.
FESS UP.

429
00:24:20,820 --> 00:24:22,920
I'LL MAKE YOU RUN
FROM HERE TO ETERNITY.

430
00:24:22,990 --> 00:24:25,220
COACH?

431
00:24:25,290 --> 00:24:27,090
BRIAN STARTED IT.

432
00:24:27,160 --> 00:24:29,330
THANK YOU, SON.
THANK YOU.

433
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:30,530
YOU CAN GET OFF
OUR FIELD NOW.

434
00:24:30,600 --> 00:24:31,900
WE APPRECIATE IT.

435
00:24:31,970 --> 00:24:34,300
ALL RIGHT? GET OUT!

436
00:24:34,370 --> 00:24:35,330
ANY MORE TRAITORS?!

437
00:24:35,400 --> 00:24:36,350
COME ON, FESS UP.

438
00:24:36,420 --> 00:24:39,640
OH, THAT'S HOW
IT'S GONNA BE, IS IT?

439
00:24:39,710 --> 00:24:41,640
YOU KNOW,
SILENCE IS A LIE, DOGS.

440
00:24:41,710 --> 00:24:43,840
IT'S A LIE OF OMISSION.

441
00:24:43,910 --> 00:24:46,810
AND IN ALABAMA...

442
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:47,900
CRIMES GET PUNISHED.

