00:25:06,400 --> 00:25:09,900
♪ LEANING, JESUS ♪

447
00:25:09,970 --> 00:25:18,090
♪ LEANING ON
THE EVERLASTING ARMS ♪

448
00:25:30,790 --> 00:25:31,860
HEY, SON!

449
00:25:31,930 --> 00:25:34,660
