WHY YOU'RE HERE,

450
00:25:34,730 --> 00:25:36,430
SO WHY DON'T YOU
JUST SAVE THE BOTH OF US

451
00:25:36,500 --> 00:25:38,630
SOME TIME AND ENERGY
AND LIMP ON OUTTA HERE.

