TO PLAY FOR YOU.

455
00:25:44,540 --> 00:25:47,010
THAT'S WHY YOU VIEW
THIS TEAM AS A THREAT.

456
00:25:47,070 --> 00:25:48,870
YOU GOT ONE THING
ON YOUR MIND:

457
00:25:48,940 --> 00:25:49,980
PLAYIN' TIME.

458
00:25:50,040 --> 00:25:52,310
I'M GONNA MAKE IT
CRYSTAL CLEAR FOR YOU:

459
00:25:52,380 --> 00:25:56,280
YOU ARE NOT GONNA PLAY
ONE MINUTE FOR ME.

460
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:10,860
[HUSHED TONE]
COACH.

461
00:26:13,500 --> 00:26:14,530
LISTEN TO ME.

462
00:26:14,600 --> 00:26:15,830
NEPHEW OR NOT,

463
00:26:15,900 --> 00:26:18,000
YOU GET TREATED THE SAME
AS EVERYONE ELSE.

464
00:26:18,070 --> 00:26:20,240
C-COACH, HOW AM I
GONNA GET A CHANCE

465
00:26:20,310 --> 00:26:21,440
AT THIS SCHOLARSHIP

466
00:26:21,510 --> 00:26:24,440
IF I DON'T GET A CHANCE
TO THROW THE BALL?

467
00:26:24,510 --> 00:26:26,980
NEVER MIND
ABOUT THE SCHOLARSHIP.

468
00:26:27,050 --> 00:26:30,120
I--YOUR NAME IS NOT
MORE IMPORTANT THAN THIS TEAM.

469
00:26:31,790 --> 00:26:34,220
IF YOU DIDN'T LEARN THAT
FROM YOUR COUSIN,

470
00:26:34,290 --> 00:26:35,820
THEN YOU GOT PROBLEMS.

471
00:26:42,260 --> 00:26:44,060
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

472
00:26:47,940 --> 00:26:49,700
I TOLD YOU.

473
00:26:49,770 --> 00:26:53,240
I WON'T PLAY SECOND
TO FOOTBALL.

474
00:26:53,310 --> 00:26:57,810
AND, UM, YOU'VE
MADE YOUR CHOICE.

475
00:26:57,880 --> 00:26:59,240
NOW LIVE WITH IT.

476
00:27:02,250 --> 00:27:04,320
YOU KNOW,
FORGET IT, OK?

477
00:27:04,390 --> 00:27:08,420
JUST...[SIGHS]

478
00:27:08,490 --> 00:27:10,260
[BELL RINGS]

479
00:27:27,740 --> 00:27:30,740
YOU'D THINK THERE WAS
A FOOTBALL GAME TONIGHT.

